WEBVTT

00:01.186 --> 00:05.225
Make sure your script is open in Digital Micrograph.

00:05.495 --> 00:08.226
Click on your script, to make sure it is selected.

00:08.564 --> 00:14.949
Go to `File > Install Script...`.

00:15.219 --> 00:36.016
Name your command and its menu in the text fields.

00:36.364 --> 00:44.354
Select either `Install for the current user only` or
`Install for all users`, depending on your needs.

00:44.856 --> 00:47.861
Click `Ok`.

00:48.473 --> 00:58.968
You may now launch your script from the menu
